15:23.590 --> 15:24.857
(sighs)

15:24.924 --> 15:26.693
I can't believe
you're arresting me.

15:26.759 --> 15:28.195
Watch your head.

15:28.261 --> 15:30.663
The real crime is what
those people are charging

15:30.730 --> 15:32.165
for a pack of gum in there.

15:32.232 --> 15:34.301
Mom, what's going on?

15:34.367 --> 15:36.503
We just caught your mother
relieving herself

15:36.569 --> 15:37.670
behind the gas station.

15:37.737 --> 15:39.939
She's being arrested
for indecent exposure.

15:40.007 --> 15:42.275
(bell dings)

15:44.611 --> 15:46.546
What am I supposed to do?
I need to find someone

15:46.613 --> 15:47.947
to pick up litter
in like five minutes.

15:48.015 --> 15:50.017
I got bigger problems, Jimmy.

15:50.083 --> 15:52.585
My mug shot's going
to look terrible.

16:02.029 --> 16:03.997
Excuse me, miss.
I'd like to pay you

16:04.064 --> 16:05.265
to pretend to be my
great-grandmother

16:05.332 --> 16:06.766
on the side of the road.

16:06.833 --> 16:07.967
It'll be dirty, but...

16:08.035 --> 16:10.437
(siren whooping)

16:12.805 --> 16:14.707
That hooker was wearing a wire.

16:14.774 --> 16:17.644
I heard the whole thing
on the walkie-talkie.

16:17.710 --> 16:19.412
It's like watching
your kid drown

16:19.479 --> 16:22.449
and not being able
to tell him to shut up.

16:22.515 --> 16:24.251
(bell dings)

16:32.225 --> 16:35.395
I know I've said lying's bad,
but, I mean,

16:35.462 --> 16:37.497
half the games we play are lies.

16:37.564 --> 16:39.466
Like peekaboo?

16:39.532 --> 16:41.501
I'm not really gone.
Still here.

16:41.568 --> 16:43.570
(cooing)

16:43.636 --> 16:46.306
What I'm saying is,
I think I have to use

16:46.373 --> 16:47.907
our neighbor's address
on this form,

16:47.974 --> 16:50.210
although I wish
I didn't have to.

16:50.277 --> 16:52.345
You know, I wouldn't have
to do all this

16:52.412 --> 16:55.115
if you weren't doing dog stuff
like barking or...

16:57.484 --> 16:59.419
Chewing bones?

16:59.486 --> 17:01.121
Who gave Hope a steak bone?

17:02.855 --> 17:04.624
She fetched my slippers.

17:04.691 --> 17:06.359
I keep my promises.

17:08.428 --> 17:09.929
(sighs):
Oh, man.

17:09.996 --> 17:11.631
(growls)

17:11.698 --> 17:12.565
(gasps)

17:13.766 --> 17:15.502
I got to get you away
from these dogs.

17:15.568 --> 17:17.504
Think I have to lie about more
than just our address.

17:18.705 --> 17:19.772
Excuse me.

17:19.839 --> 17:21.741
Everybody?

17:21.808 --> 17:25.145
I would like to thank
you all for applying.

17:25.212 --> 17:28.215
All of you had
such compelling stories.

17:28.281 --> 17:30.117
The O'Donnells.

17:30.183 --> 17:32.051
Both of you working three jobs

17:32.119 --> 17:34.621
while living
in another family's basement,

17:34.687 --> 17:38.024
somehow using a hot plate
to heat your bathwater.

17:38.091 --> 17:39.259
Oh, and Mr. Melman.

17:39.326 --> 17:40.893
Mr. Melman volunteers

17:40.960 --> 17:44.431
every single day
in a downtown soup kitchen.

17:45.865 --> 17:48.535
The Sanchezes had to float
to this country

17:48.601 --> 17:50.036
on an inner tube
with nothing but a stick

17:50.103 --> 17:51.704
to fight off the shark attacks.

17:53.473 --> 17:56.176
Oh, and the Hassecks,
who are functionally mute.

17:58.911 --> 18:01.348
But one story stood out.

18:01.414 --> 18:03.416
Would you come up here,
Jim Chance?

18:03.483 --> 18:06.553
Come on.
Don't be shy.

18:09.822 --> 18:12.292
James Chance,

18:12.359 --> 18:15.762
single father who gave up
a promising career in art

18:15.828 --> 18:18.231
to fight for his country
in Afghanistan,

18:18.298 --> 18:20.433
only to injure
his drawing hand

18:20.500 --> 18:22.169
while carrying several
orphans to safety.

18:22.235 --> 18:24.404
Then, when he
came back,

18:24.471 --> 18:27.006
he was carjacked by a
man desperate for money

18:27.073 --> 18:30.243
to pay for a
kidney transplant.

18:30.310 --> 18:33.079
And who do you suppose
gave him the kidney?

18:33.146 --> 18:35.014
ALL:
James Chance.

18:35.081 --> 18:37.950
The scholarship goes
to Hope Chance.

18:38.017 --> 18:39.719
Congratulations.

18:39.786 --> 18:41.688
Yeah, I-I'm sorry
to have to do this,

18:41.754 --> 18:43.756
but the "unchosen" will
have to leave now.

18:43.823 --> 18:45.525
Thank you.

18:45.592 --> 18:47.227
Just... mm-hmm.

18:49.162 --> 18:50.897
Thank you.

18:50.963 --> 18:52.332
Wait.

18:53.500 --> 18:55.568
I lied on my application.

18:55.635 --> 18:58.271
What?
I lied on my application.

18:58.338 --> 18:59.939
I didn't even want to lie,

19:00.006 --> 19:02.509
but it all started when...
when I had to fake my address

19:02.575 --> 19:03.910
because we have blue dots.

19:03.976 --> 19:05.745
We're... we're
sexual offenders.

19:05.812 --> 19:07.214
Excuse me?

19:07.280 --> 19:09.249
But it's all
a misunderstanding, right?

19:09.316 --> 19:10.650
My parents hooked up
as teenagers,

19:10.717 --> 19:13.186
my great-grandmother runs around
without her bra on,

19:13.253 --> 19:15.355
and I tried to get a favor
from a hooker.

19:15.422 --> 19:17.690
Okay, but it wasn't
a sexual favor.

19:18.925 --> 19:21.794
I really wanted to get my
daughter into this school.

19:21.861 --> 19:23.763
I'm sorry.

19:25.031 --> 19:28.235
Uh... I'm really sorry.

19:29.702 --> 19:32.339
That was very brave,
Mr. Chance.

19:32.405 --> 19:35.041
Coming clean like that,
that took courage.

19:35.107 --> 19:36.976
Really?

19:37.043 --> 19:38.378
Cool.

19:38.445 --> 19:39.479
Wait. Wait,
wait, wait.

19:39.546 --> 19:41.348
I can be brave, too.

19:41.414 --> 19:43.350
I don't really volunteer
at the soup kitchen.

19:43.416 --> 19:45.418
I have OCD--
one, two, three, four, five--

19:45.485 --> 19:47.487
and... and I think
that homeless people are filthy.

19:47.554 --> 19:48.855
One, two, three, four, five.

19:48.921 --> 19:51.157
Uh, we didn't really come here
on an inner tube.

19:51.224 --> 19:53.025
Sure, our name is Sanchez,

19:53.092 --> 19:55.962
but we're about as Latino
as the Three Amigos.

19:56.028 --> 19:57.397
Uh, we can speak.

19:57.464 --> 19:59.399
In fact, my wife here
will hardly ever shut up.

19:59.466 --> 20:00.933
And she hits me.

20:01.000 --> 20:01.901
JIMMY:
Hey.

20:01.968 --> 20:03.403
I also lied
about my kid's mother.

20:03.470 --> 20:04.637
She was a serial killer.

20:04.704 --> 20:06.072
I didn't even get into that.

20:06.138 --> 20:07.874
Yeah, my penis is tiny.

20:07.940 --> 20:09.075
Okay, uh-uh.

20:09.141 --> 20:11.210
JIMMY:
Honesty may be the best policy,

20:11.278 --> 20:13.980
but in this case,
it got us all disqualified.

20:14.046 --> 20:15.181
It also gave me a chance

20:15.248 --> 20:17.250
to tell everyone
about Shelley's day care,

20:17.317 --> 20:19.586
and honestly,
I couldn't be happier.

20:20.853 --> 20:22.389
Wow, Jimmy.

20:23.756 --> 20:26.693
Thanks for telling so many
people about my school.

20:26.759 --> 20:28.261
This place is great.

20:28.328 --> 20:30.330
It just needed
more kids.

20:30.397 --> 20:31.931
Okay, everybody,

20:31.998 --> 20:34.567
I think we're ready to
sing the welcome song.

20:37.304 --> 20:39.739
* Yesterday I was so lonely *

20:39.806 --> 20:41.808
* Nothing but Kibbles 'n Bits *

20:41.874 --> 20:44.577
* Just me and the dogs,
they chewed up my clogs *

20:44.644 --> 20:47.747
* And one had a case of the... *

20:47.814 --> 20:49.081
* Poopies *

20:49.148 --> 20:51.584
* But today I made *

20:51.651 --> 20:54.321
* New best friends,
new best friends *

20:54.387 --> 20:56.989
* It's only been a minute,
but we're new best friends *

20:57.056 --> 20:59.859
* Sisters and bros,
nuevo amigos *

20:59.926 --> 21:02.329
* Sharing our secrets
till every day ends *

21:02.395 --> 21:03.863
Everybody!

21:03.930 --> 21:06.733
* New best friends,
new best friends *

21:06.799 --> 21:09.369
* We just met this morning,
but we're new best friends *

21:09.436 --> 21:11.904
* Sisters and bros,
nuevo amigos *

21:11.971 --> 21:14.641
* Sharing our secrets
till every day ends *
(doorbell rings)

21:14.707 --> 21:17.344
* New best friends... *

21:17.410 --> 21:19.011
We're the Chances.

21:19.078 --> 21:20.347
We're all sex offenders

21:20.413 --> 21:21.614
living in your neighborhood.

21:21.681 --> 21:24.684
Except me. I'm clean.

21:24.751 --> 21:27.019
BOY:
Keep your shirt on, Maw Maw.
